gnu.trove

Class TDecorators

  • java.lang.Object
    • gnu.trove.TDecorators

  • public class TDecorators
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a static utility class that provides functions for simplifying creation of decorators.
    Since:
    Trove 2.1
